OL,3,CHermit crabs 'using plastic waste for
OL,4,Cshells'
OL,6,FHermit crab species are increasingly
OL,7,Fchoosing to use discarded plastic
OL,8,Fwaste as a protective armour for their
OL,9,Fbodies over shells, a study has found.
OL,11,FScientists published their research in
OL,12,Fthe journal and found that 10 of 16
OL,13,Fterrestrial hermit crab types exhibit
OL,14,Fthis behaviour globally.
OL,16,FThey used a research method, known as
OL,17,FiEcology (internet Ecology), which
OL,18,Fanalyses photos, published on digital
OL,19,Fplatforms - including Google and Flikr
OL,20,F- by wildlife enthusiasts.
