OL,3,CHermit crabs 'using plastic waste for
OL,4,Cshells'
OL,6,FTypically, hermit crabs scavenge
OL,7,Fshells from gastropods (molluscs) for
OL,8,Ftheir protection from predators, while
OL,9,Fprevious studies have found that the
OL,10,Fanimals' choice can play an important
OL,11,Frole when females choose which males
OL,12,Fto mate with.
OL,14,FBut the study identified a growing
OL,15,Ftrend of the crabs now choosing
OL,16,Fartificial shells, along the majority
OL,17,Fof tropical coastlines in both
OL,18,Fhemispheres.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/7
