OL,3,CHermit crabs 'using plastic waste for
OL,4,Cshells'
OL,6,FSome 386 photographs were identified
OL,7,Fin the research as showing a hermit
OL,8,Fcrab wearing an artificial shell, of
OL,9,Fwhich the majority (84.5%) were made
OL,10,Fout of plastic - such as bottle caps.
OL,12,FMetal and glass were the other most
OL,13,Fcommon materials identified as
OL,14,Fartificial shells.
OL,16,FResearchers Marta Szulkin, Zuzanna
OL,17,FJagiello and Lukasz Dylewski
OL,18,Fhypothesised a number of theories for
OL,19,Ftheir findings.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/7
