OL,3,CHermit crabs 'using plastic waste for
OL,4,Cshells'
OL,6,FThey suggested that a simultaneous
OL,7,Frise in global plastic pollution
OL,8,Falongside declining mollusc
OL,9,Fpopulations were to blame.
OL,11,FHermit crabs could also choose
OL,12,Fartificial shells for their protection
OL,13,Fas a point of preference, although the
OL,14,Fresearchers stressed scientific
OL,15,Fstudies have yet to explore the weight
OL,16,Fof this theory.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/7
