OL,3,CHermit crabs 'using plastic waste for
OL,4,Cshells'
OL,6,FThe trend, meanwhile, could have
OL,7,Fevolutionary implications for hermit
OL,8,Fcrabs, the researchers concluded, and
OL,9,Fhas opened up new questions around how
OL,10,Fthe animals interact with discarded
OL,11,Fhuman waste.
OL,13,FHermit crabs have evolved to scavenge
OL,14,Ffor gastropod shells which, when in
OL,15,Fshort supply, are fought over by
OL,16,Fcompeting crabs.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
