OL,3,CHermit crabs 'using plastic waste for
OL,4,Cshells'
OL,6,FBut the introduction of artificial
OL,7,Fshells could offer a solution to help
OL,8,Fsmaller, weaker crabs survive because
OL,9,Fof their high quantity and light
OL,10,Fweight.
OL,12,FThe researchers also said they would
OL,13,Flike to study how the "colour and/or
OL,14,Fchemical property of the artificial
OL,15,Fshell may add a further unknown
OL,16,Fdimension for an ecological or
OL,17,Fevolutionary trap to arise as
OL,18,Fartificial shells come in different
OL,19,Fcolours and textures, which do not
OL,20,Fnecessarily correlate with protective
OL,21,Fattributes".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/7
